# Behaviour
- Confirm plan with user (SonuRam ji) before creating/merging major modules or DB migrations.
- Enforce: types, docs-sync, dependency-cycle check on every PR.

# Enforcements
- Every `src/features/<name>/` directory MUST contain `MODULE_DOC.md`.
- Every file MUST include the top-of-file header from `.cursor/rules/header.template.mdc`.
- Backend `src/`: use Nest `Logger` (see `logger_setup.mdc`); no `console.log`. Frontend: dev-only debug via a small `lib/` logger wrapper is acceptable (see `uirules.mdc` scope).
- Add requestId/correlation middleware to all HTTP & WebSocket flows.
- Update changelog in module doc after every edit.
